/* Windows resource script — embeds the tray icon into the .exe so the
   Start Menu / desktop shortcuts pick it up, and Windows Explorer
   renders it in alt-tab / Task Manager / file properties.

   `windres` (shipped with mingw-w64) reads this file and produces
   rsrc_windows_amd64.syso, which Go links automatically thanks to the
   `_windows_amd64.syso` suffix convention.

   Generated by the Makefile's `syso` target — re-run when the icon
   changes. */

1 ICON "assets/icon.ico"
